The '''Alliance War Museum''' was an institution dedicated to the exhibition and preservation of artifacts and information related to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance's]] military efforts during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

Located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], the majority of its items were either donated by former Alliance members or recovered by [[Operation Flotsam]] under the [[Historical Battle Site Preservation Act]], which also funded the museum. Its curators were aggressive in acquiring well-known items, and harassed [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] for years to donate the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']].

